==Hindi==

===Alternative spellings===
*[[चांपना]]

===Etymology===
From the Old Indo-Aryan roots ćāṅp˚ (= ćāp˚) through the [[Prakrit]] चंपाइ and Sanskrit चपय(ति), rt. चप्

===Transitive verb===
'''चाँपना''' ''cāṅpanā'', ''cãpanā'' or ''chāmpnā'' 

# To press, squeeze, to knead 
# to [[shampoo]]
# to thrust in, stuff, cram

